<item>
            <title>[HBASE-6037] Have a separate hbase-xxx.xml property file that only has client side configuration settings.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-6037</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It would be good to have a separate hbase-xxx.xml (hbase-client.xml perhaps) file that only contains settings relevant to hbase clients.  This would allow &quot;secrets&quot; to be present in the hbase-site.xml file, and also have a smaller config for clients that may be decoupled from the hmaster and regionservers.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12556276">HBASE-6037</key>
            <summary>Have a separate hbase-xxx.xml property file that only has client side configuration settings.</summary>
