                            <comment id="13278237" author="stack" created="Thu, 17 May 2012 20:42:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;What about fact that servers use &apos;clients&apos; too.  Would we have to have the hbase-client.xml out on cluster as well?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13278404" author="jmhsieh" created="Thu, 17 May 2012 23:43:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I would think that the servers would have both files and the clients would only need the client side one.  At the moment this is just an idea &amp;#8211; I recently ran into similar problems in hdfs land and suggested a similar kind of fix to a committer over there.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
